      "text": "Following Phase 27's configuration consolidation, Exaix still has scattered environment variable usage across production and testing contexts. This phase aims to:\n\n1. **Retain essential runtime overrides** (`EXA_LLM_*`) for CLI/TUI flexibility\n2. **Retire redundant production env vars** that duplicate `exa.config.toml` functionality\n3. **Standardize testing env vars** to use `EXA_TEST_*` prefix for clarity\n4. **Implement Zod validation** for all environment variable inputs\n5. **Document all supported env vars** in `exa.config.sample.toml`\n\n**Scope:** No deprecation period. This is a breaking change for Phase 28.\n\n---\n\n## Goals",
